com.inchok.aria2

Class Aria2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inchok.aria2.Aria2

  • public class Aria2
extends java.lang.Object
    The static class which operates the global operations. Before you do anything with Aria2, you must call Aria2.initialize() first to initialize. After you finish your task, you need to call Aria2.deInitialize() to release the static global resources.
    Version:
    Version 1.0
    Author:
    inCHOK
    See Also:
    initialize(), deInitialize()
